::KitKat::

She saw Quickstrike motion to them to go over to his position.
"He is waving to us."  She walked over to Quickstrike.  "Are you badly 
damaged?  Do you need assistance? You don't look to good.  Where is your 
base and I'll help you get back there."  She was concerned for this brave 
bot.  She looked at the other female.  She raised her voice so she could 
hear her. "He's going to need help back to your base."
